It’s been six months today since we exchanged rings and officially got to call each other Mrs. Sharma and Mr. Jangra (hehehe).

In these past six months, we’ve argued, made up, shared love, travelled, checked off things from each other’s bucket lists—and most importantly, we’ve never forgotten to respect one another.

The love and affection you shower on me feels like an aura I never want to step out of. These months have flown by, and I want to spend the rest of my life with you just like this.

I love you to the moon and back my love my ghughu ❤️❤️
